 // it to call futex(2) with bogus op arguments. To workaround this, we need
 // to allow those futex(2) calls to fail with EINVAL, instead of crashing the
@@ -236,9 +251,11 @@ ResultExpr RestrictFcntlCommands() {
   // operator.
